    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389290/extras/69c13aeb3b8f70c104ec585dd170761d.poster.avif?t=1718157691\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389290/extras/69c13aeb3b8f70c104ec585dd170761d.webm?t=1718157691\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389290/extras/69c13aeb3b8f70c104ec585dd170761d.mp4?t=1718157691\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Please</strong> is a VR top-down rhythm RPG - while exploring the story, enjoy various rhythm minigames that are a homage to the large rhythm game genres!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389290/extras/81c97411ffd860a692451529179c8e80.webp?t=1718157691\" width=616 height=16 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389290/extras/ac8a3adad1fd5279b7253ccb863d863a.poster.avif?t=1718157691\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389290/extras/ac8a3adad1fd5279b7253ccb863d863a.webm?t=1718157691\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389290/extras/ac8a3adad1fd5279b7253ccb863d863a.mp4?t=1718157691\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>During bullet hell Boss Battles, protect your avatar by dodging attacks and using your physical hands to block them!<br></li><li>Play rhythm minigames that pay an homage to the genre, such as drum hitting, notes falling from the sky, blindly following orders from some random person, etc!<br></li><li>Solve puzzles that require controlling your avatar, using your hands, or both!<br></li><li>Explore the mysteries of this world, learn about various character's stories and how their Traumas affect them!</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389290/extras/c759e242b9844d522f21d24db623c638.webp?t=1718157691\" width=616 height=16 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >World</h2>Traverse a mysterious world of in-between with a variety of residents. These residents seem to be stuck in this world due to their lingering attachment to their Trauma - get to know them, play minigames with them, and eventually defend yourself against their minds! Figure out what role you play in this world - and the mysteries behind it.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389290/extras/89fef45ec8ad241b70a7005d51d97d26.poster.avif?t=1718157691\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389290/extras/89fef45ec8ad241b70a7005d51d97d26.webm?t=1718157691\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389290/extras/89fef45ec8ad241b70a7005d51d97d26.mp4?t=1718157691\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The different art styles play into the story of the game; pixel art and low poly art are objects considered in the game world in which your avatar can interact with, while realistic art objects are ones that came from another world and able to interacted with your real hands! How did these foreign looking realistic objects come to this world? Why are you the only one able to interact with it?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389290/extras/81c97411ffd860a692451529179c8e80.webp?t=1718157691\" width=616 height=16 /></span><br><br>Join our community on Discord - we're also looking for VR playtesters, pixel artists and generalist modelers!<br><br><br><br>Thank you for checking out our game!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389290/extras/8953ccae1e6fd2a4b4f231a59a8c4e72.apng?t=1718157691\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389290/extras/8953ccae1e6fd2a4b4f231a59a8c4e72.poster.avif?t=1718157691\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=96 /></picture></span>",
